  "body": "### Component\n\nForge, Cast, Other (please describe)\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\ncurrently `forge` use 99 as default chain ID (inherited from dapptools), geth --dev and ganache use `1337`, hardhat uses `31337`\r\n\r\n#1037 also currently uses `1337`.\r\n\r\nI think we should unify this for forge + anvil and not introduce a completely new chain, this leaves us with 3 options\r\n- 1337\r\n- 99\r\n- 31337\r\n\r\n1337 is already marked as `Dev` chain in the `Chain` enum type. \n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
